snippet.title: Warhaven: Biggest Changes Revealed | gamescom 2023
snippet.description: Stella Chung sat down with Game Director Eunseok Yi to discuss some of the biggest changes being made to Nexon's upcoming massive medieval combat game Warhaven. What new changes can we expect in multiplayer squads, and what can we expect from future content, with it being a free-to-play game? Find out all this and more as we kick off gamescom studio Opening Night Live!
